with cornflour and have deep fried it giving it a nice texture and flavour
further we have cooked it in the manchurian sauce this paneer manchurian is
super quick and easy to make it is versatile you can have it as an appetizer
or also as a side dish along with fried rice or hakka noodles
paneer a few other commonly available ingredients and a few minutes is all
